As for juvenile <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">offenders</ENAMEX>, <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">between 1989 and 1993</TIMEX>, the number of adjudicated
juvenile cases that resulted in probation rose by <NUMEX TYPE="PERCENT">17 percent</NUMEX>. The number of
