<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">officers</ENAMEX> with local police <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">officers</ENAMEX>. Patrolling the <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC_DESC">streets</ENAMEX> together, they have
