serious efforts to reinvent probation and parole, and time to debate fresh
ideas. After all, we are not going to put every convicted <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">adult</ENAMEX> and juvenile
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">felon</ENAMEX> behind bars and keep him or her there--nor should we.

         
      
   
